# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# User-generated credentials & secrets -- NEVER commit (public repo).
# Every app regenerates these on first use, so they don't belong in git.
# Anchored to the SD mirror and globbed (**/) for safety.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# WiFi credentials (WiFiManager)
wifi.json
**/wifi.json
# Credential-encryption PIN hash (secure_creds)
cred_pin.json
**/cred_pin.json
# Anthropic API key / Claude.ai OAuth token (Remote Claude)
claude.json
**/claude.json
# SSH client: saved profiles (encrypted passwords) + trusted host keys
ssh_profiles.json
**/ssh_profiles.json
ssh_known_hosts.json
**/ssh_known_hosts.json
# SSH server: private host key, login hash, authorized public keys
ssh_host_ecdsa.json
**/ssh_host_ecdsa.json
ssh_server.json
**/ssh_server.json
authorized_keys
**/authorized_keys
# Generic key/secret material
*.pem
*.key
# User scan / log data (ProxiScan, sub-GHz)
MicroPython/sd/scan_logs/
MicroPython/sd/subghz_logs/
